(274, '_transient_dash_4077549d03da2e451c8b5f002294ff51', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wordpress.org/news/2014/12/dinah/''>WordPress 4.1 “Dinah”</a> <span class="rss-date">18 december 2014</span><div class="rssSummary">Version 4.1 of WordPress, named “Dinah” in honor of jazz singer Dinah Washington, is available for download or update in your WordPress dashboard. New features in WordPress 4.1 help you focus on your writing, and the new default theme lets you show it off in style. Introducing Twenty Fifteen Our newest default theme, Twenty Fifteen, is [&hellip;]</div></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/thank-a-plugin-author-day-2015''>WPTavern: Thank a Plugin Author Day 2015</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/envato-stats-tips-for-getting-things-done-and-more-at-pressnomics-3''>WPTavern: Envato Stats, Tips For Getting Things Done, and More at PressNomics 3</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://ma.tt/2015/01/kitchensink-wp-podcast/''>Matt: Kitchensink WP podcast</a></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li class=''dashboard-news-plugin''><span>Populaire plugin:</span> <a href=''https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce/'' class=''dashboard-news-plugin-link''>WooCommerce - excelling eCommerce</a>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=woocommerce&amp;_wpnonce=7795c93861&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''WooCommerce - excelling eCommerce''>Installeren</a>)</span></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
